OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnsafe housing to see      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fproviders' funding stripped
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Housing providers that fail to address 
OL,6, safety and quality concerns will be    
OL,7, blocked from new government funding as 
OL,8, part of a crackdown on poor standards. 
OL,10,FIt comes after a coroner ruled that the
OL,11,Fdeath of toddler Awaab Ishak was caused
OL,12,Fby exposure to mould in his home.      
OL,14,FAs part of the new measures, the       
OL,15,Fassociation involved, Rochdale         
OL,16,FBoroughwide Housing (RBH), will not    
OL,17,Freceive #1m of expected funding.       
OL,19,FHousing Secretary Michael Gove said it 
OL,20,Fshould serve as a "warning" to others. 
